data.description: Welcome to Arrowhead.  Enjoy this spacious, open floor plan home, complete with pool, hot tub and beautiful outdoor living area.  This house includes 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The bedrooms are located on the left side of the house as you enter and the living spaces on the right. This home also includes a large laundry room with plenty of storage space as well an extremely generous pantry.  The living room fireplace is a nice touch and will make for cozy winter nights.  Come make this one yours, and enjoy all the conveniences of living in Arrowhead.
